      <title>linux-ntp</title>
      <link href="/2020/03/29/linux-ntp/"/>
      <url>/2020/03/29/linux-ntp/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>在網際網路中，系統上線前，最重要的作業莫過於對時了：<br>Linux 的設定中，在 CentOS7 版本之後採用 chrony 為 NTP 的工具<br>在安裝完 chrony package 後即可使用 NTP 的工具</p><a id="more"></a><h2 id="NTP-Server-chronyd"><a href="#NTP-Server-chronyd" class="headerlink" title="NTP Server chronyd"></a>NTP Server chronyd</h2><p>設定 NTP server 使用 chronyd 服務，設定檔案為 <code>/etc/chrony.conf</code><br>可以編輯此檔案，將檔案內的 server xxxx 修改為自己的 server 即可在內網使用</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Use public servers from the pool.ntp.org project.</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Please consider joining the pool (http://www.pool.ntp.org/join.html).</span></span><br><span class="line">server 0.centos.pool.ntp.org iburst</span><br><span class="line">server 1.centos.pool.ntp.org iburst</span><br><span class="line">server 2.centos.pool.ntp.org iburst</span><br><span class="line">server 3.centos.pool.ntp.org iburst</span><br><span class="line">...</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>修改為</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">server &lt;內網中的 NTP Server1&gt; iburst</span><br><span class="line">server &lt;內網中的 NTP Server2&gt; iburst</span><br><span class="line">server &lt;內網中的 NTP Server3&gt; iburst</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>建議設定三部的 NTP 主機，NTP 的架構可以由主要的 core switch 來負責，有時間時再來討論。<br>修改完成後重新啟動 chrony daemon (chronyd.service) 即可</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">systemctl <span class="built_in">enable</span> chronyd.service</span><br><span class="line">systemctl start chronyd.service</span><br><span class="line">systemctl status chronyd.service</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="NTP-Client-chronyc"><a href="#NTP-Client-chronyc" class="headerlink" title="NTP Client chronyc"></a>NTP Client chronyc</h2><p>在 Linux 中，相同程式碼如果後綴的字元為 <code>c</code> 的指令常常是 command line 的指令。<br>例如在 chrony 套件中 chronyc 即是 command line 的指令<br>後綴的字元為 <code>d</code> 的指令通常為服務 <code>daemon</code> 如 chronyd</p><h3 id="檢查-sources"><a href="#檢查-sources" class="headerlink" title="檢查 sources"></a>檢查 sources</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[root@nagios code]<span class="comment"># chronyc sources</span></span><br><span class="line">210 Number of sources = 4</span><br><span class="line">MS Name/IP address         Stratum Poll Reach LastRx Last sample               </span><br><span class="line">===============================================================================</span><br><span class="line">^- static.80.158.217.95.cli&gt;     2   6   177    33  +1205us[+1205us] +/-  161ms</span><br><span class="line">^+ static.home.twn.sciurida&gt;     2   6   177    33  -2235us[+4055us] +/-   18ms</span><br><span class="line">^- time.cloudflare.com           3   6   177    34  +6601us[  +13ms] +/-   80ms</span><br><span class="line">^* bom-gw.tipsy.coffee           2   6   177    33  +1593us[+3613us] +/- 7125us</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="檢查-tracking"><a href="#檢查-tracking" class="headerlink" title="檢查 tracking"></a>檢查 tracking</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[root@nagios code]<span class="comment"># chronyc tracking</span></span><br><span class="line">Reference ID    : 76A3AA06 (bom-gw.tipsy.coffee)</span><br><span class="line">Stratum         : 3</span><br><span class="line">Ref time (UTC)  : Sun Mar 29 07:23:55 2020</span><br><span class="line">System time     : 0.000000044 seconds fast of NTP time</span><br><span class="line">Last offset     : +0.002020220 seconds</span><br><span class="line">RMS offset      : 0.004714346 seconds</span><br><span class="line">Frequency       : 19.275 ppm slow</span><br><span class="line">Residual freq   : +0.613 ppm</span><br><span class="line">Skew            : 31.625 ppm</span><br><span class="line">Root delay      : 0.012406345 seconds</span><br><span class="line">Root dispersion : 0.003200516 seconds</span><br><span class="line">Update interval : 0.2 seconds</span><br><span class="line">Leap status     : Normal</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="手動對時"><a href="#手動對時" class="headerlink" title="手動對時"></a>手動對時</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[root@nagios code]<span class="comment"># chronyc makestep</span></span><br><span class="line">200 OK</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>對時完成後再檢查一下 tracking 看看對時後的結果:</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[root@nagios code]<span class="comment"># chronyc tracking</span></span><br><span class="line">Reference ID    : 76A3AA06 (bom-gw.tipsy.coffee)</span><br><span class="line">Stratum         : 3</span><br><span class="line">Ref time (UTC)  : Sun Mar 29 07:26:04 2020</span><br><span class="line">System time     : 0.000000000 seconds slow of NTP time</span><br><span class="line">Last offset     : +0.001181512 seconds</span><br><span class="line">RMS offset      : 0.004281717 seconds</span><br><span class="line">Frequency       : 10.007 ppm slow</span><br><span class="line">Residual freq   : +0.424 ppm</span><br><span class="line">Skew            : 16.726 ppm</span><br><span class="line">Root delay      : 0.012622609 seconds</span><br><span class="line">Root dispersion : 0.002506560 seconds</span><br><span class="line">Update interval : 65.0 seconds</span><br><span class="line">Leap status     : Normal</span><br><span class="line">[root@nagios code]<span class="comment">#</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="source-state-對時主機的狀態"><a href="#source-state-對時主機的狀態" class="headerlink" title="source state 對時主機的狀態"></a>source state 對時主機的狀態</h3><p>列出 NTP 對時主機的狀態</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[root@nagios code]<span class="comment"># chronyc sourcestate</span></span><br><span class="line">210 Number of sources = 4</span><br><span class="line">Name/IP Address            NP  NR  Span  Frequency  Freq Skew  Offset  Std Dev</span><br><span class="line">==============================================================================</span><br><span class="line">static.80.158.217.95.cli&gt;  10   5  1165     +0.252      0.137   +529us    32us</span><br><span class="line">static.home.twn.sciurida&gt;   8   5   453     -3.604     15.916  -1453us   984us</span><br><span class="line">time.cloudflare.com        22  12   23m     -0.983      2.546  +5261us  1288us</span><br><span class="line">bom-gw.tipsy.coffee         9   7   649     +0.002      0.120  +1028ns    15us</span><br><span class="line">[root@nagios code]<span class="comment">#</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
