        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<blockquote class="blockquote-center">            <p><a href="#演練2">演練2</a></p>          </blockquote><a id="more"></a><h2 id="演練2"><a href="#演練2" class="headerlink" title="演練2"></a>演練2</h2><p>協助客戶進行一次演練，遇到一些狀況，也就這樣忙了一整天，<br>還將一位好友拖下水，處理了好一陣子。<br>最後總算完成了還原。還有另外一個明天繼續。<br>雖然花了些時間，總算搞懂了一些觀念。<br>問題一 速度問題，看起來與平台間採用的通信演算法有關<br><a href="https://www.extrahop.com/company/blog/2016/tcp-nodelay-nagle-quickack-best-practices/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Nagle‘s Algorithm, 與Delayed ACK 間的衝突有關</a></p><p>Reference for AIX:<a href="https://www.ibm.com/support/knowledgecenter/en/ssw_aix_72/performance/tcp_nodelay_tcp_nagle_limit.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">The tcp_nodelay or tcp_nagle_limit options</a><br><a href="https://www.ibm.com/support/knowledgecenter/en/SSTFXA_6.3.0/com.ibm.itm.doc_6.3/install/platformrec_one.htm" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Disabling TCP-delayed acknowledgments on AIX systems</a><br><a href="https://www.ibm.com/support/pages/aix-how-fast-my-nic" target="_blank" rel="noopener">In AIX, how fast is my NIC?</a></p>]]></content>
      
      
