    <entry>
      <title>修改 hexo 的字體設定 引用 Google Font 為外部字體</title>
      <link href="/2020/03/24/hexo-external-fonts/"/>
      <url>/2020/03/24/hexo-external-fonts/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Hexo NexT 已支援外部字型，目前以 google font 為來進行設置<br>由於剛開始使用的 NexT 與後來更新的版本不同，列出兩個版本的設定方式:</p><a id="more"></a><h1 id="更新-NexT-7-x-的修改方式"><a href="#更新-NexT-7-x-的修改方式" class="headerlink" title="更新 NexT 7.x 的修改方式"></a>更新 NexT 7.x 的修改方式</h1><h2 id="直接修改-theme-next-config-yml-檔案"><a href="#直接修改-theme-next-config-yml-檔案" class="headerlink" title="直接修改 theme/next/_config.yml 檔案"></a>直接修改 theme/next/_config.yml 檔案</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">font:</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="built_in">enable</span>: <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># Uri of fonts host, e.g. https://fonts.googleapis.com (Default).</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># 如果是 Google 就保留空白，否則會有問題</span></span><br><span class="line">  host:</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># Font options:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># `external: true` will load this font family from `host` above.</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># `family: Times New Roman`. Without any quotes.</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># `size: x.x`. Use `em` as unit. Default: 1 (16px)</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># Global font settings used for all elements inside &lt;body&gt;.</span></span><br><span class="line">  global:</span><br><span class="line">    external: <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">    family: Noto Serif TC</span><br><span class="line">    size: 1.2</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># 其他字型的設定也是相同方式進行設定, size: 可以為 1.2 (加大)</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># Font settings for site title (.site-title).</span></span><br><span class="line">  title:</span><br><span class="line">    external: <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">    family: Noto Serif TC</span><br><span class="line">    size: 1.2</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># Font settings for headlines (&lt;h1&gt; to &lt;h6&gt;).</span></span><br><span class="line">  headings:</span><br><span class="line">    external: <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">    family: Noto Serif TC</span><br><span class="line">    size: 1.2</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># Font settings for posts (.post-body).</span></span><br><span class="line">  posts:</span><br><span class="line">    external: <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">    family: Noto Serif TC</span><br><span class="line">    size: 1.1</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># Font settings for &lt;code&gt; and code blocks.</span></span><br><span class="line">  codes:</span><br><span class="line">    external: <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">    family: Courier New</span><br><span class="line">    size: 1.2</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>如果要新增或是擴充其他自訂的效果<br>可在 <code>themes/next/source/css/</code> 目錄下新增一個 _custom 的子目錄，建立一個 <code>themes/next/source/css/_custom/custom.styl</code> 檔案，將您要加入的樣式寫入此 <code>custom.styl</code> 內<br>設定好 custom 的 style 後並不會生效，要將這個新增的設定引入原來架構的設定檔中</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">theme\next\<span class="built_in">source</span>\css\-main.styl           // 主設定檔</span><br><span class="line">                     +-_colors.styl</span><br><span class="line">                     +-_mixins.styl</span><br><span class="line">                     +_schemes/            // schema 相關框架目錄</span><br><span class="line">                     +_common/</span><br><span class="line">                     +_variables/          // 主要的 css 設定目錄</span><br><span class="line">                     +_custom/             // 新增的 css 設定目錄</span><br><span class="line">                     +_custom/-custom.styl</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>在主設定檔加入自訂的設定檔：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">@import <span class="string">"_custom/custom.styl"</span>;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>加入的樣式 css 寫入此 <code>custom.styl</code> 內<br>custom.styl 的內容如下</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">```</span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># NexT 5.x 的修改方式</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">## 修改字體</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">修改配置文件中的參數</span><br><span class="line">修改配置文件 _config.yml ，找到font將下列代碼中紅色的部分修改成綠色的部分即可。可以根據實際情況稍作修改！ 文件位置: `./themes/next/_config.yml`</span><br><span class="line">``` bash</span><br><span class="line">font:</span><br><span class="line">- <span class="built_in">enable</span>: <span class="literal">false</span></span><br><span class="line">+ <span class="built_in">enable</span>: <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># Uri of fonts host, e.g. //fonts.googleapis.com (Default).</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># Uri字體主機，例如//fonts.googleapis.com（默認）。</span></span><br><span class="line">+ host: https://fonts.loli.net</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># Font options:字體選項：</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># `external: true` will load this font family from `host` above.</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># `family: Times New Roman`. Without any quotes.</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># `size: xx`. Use `px` as unit.</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># Global font settings used for all elements in &lt;body&gt;.</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># 用於&lt;body&gt;中所有元素的全局字體設置。</span></span><br><span class="line">  global:</span><br><span class="line">    external: <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">+  family: Noto Serif TC</span><br><span class="line">    size:</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># Font settings for Headlines (H1, H2, H3, H4, H5, H6).</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># 標題的字體設置（H1，H2，H3，H4，H5，H6）。</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># Fallback to `global` font settings.</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># 回退到`global`字體設置。</span></span><br><span class="line">  headings:</span><br><span class="line">    external: <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">+  family: Noto Serif TC</span><br><span class="line">    size:</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># Font settings for posts.帖子的字體設置</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># Fallback to `global` font settings.回退到`global`字體設置。</span></span><br><span class="line">  posts:</span><br><span class="line">    external: <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">+  family: Noto Serif TC</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># Font settings for Logo.LOGO的字體設置。</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># Fallback to `global` font settings.回退到`global`字體設置。</span></span><br><span class="line">  logo:</span><br><span class="line">    external: <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">+  family: Noto Serif TC</span><br><span class="line">    size:</span><br><span class="line">``` </span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">## 修改配置文件</span></span><br><span class="line">找到 theme 的base.styl文件，位置在 `themes/next/<span class="built_in">source</span>/css/_variables/base.styl`,然後修改設定如下</span><br><span class="line">``` bash </span><br><span class="line">-<span class="variable">$font</span>-family-monospace    = consolas, Menlo, <span class="variable">$font</span>-family-chinese, monospace</span><br><span class="line">+<span class="variable">$font</span>-family-monospace    = consolas, Menlo, <span class="variable">$font</span>-family-base, monospace</span><br><span class="line">-<span class="variable">$font</span>-family-monospace    = get_font_family(<span class="string">'codes'</span>), consolas, Menlo, <span class="variable">$font</span>-family-chinese, monospace <span class="keyword">if</span> get_font_family(<span class="string">'codes'</span>)</span><br><span class="line">+<span class="variable">$font</span>-family-monospace    = get_font_family(<span class="string">'codes'</span>), consolas, Menlo, <span class="variable">$font</span>-family-base, monospace <span class="keyword">if</span> get_font_family(<span class="string">'codes'</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="自定義項目-設置字體大小"><a href="#自定義項目-設置字體大小" class="headerlink" title="自定義項目:設置字體大小"></a>自定義項目:設置字體大小</h2><p>修改字體 size, 文件位置:<code>./themes/next/source/css/_variables/base.styl</code></p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">// Font size</span><br><span class="line"><span class="variable">$font</span>-size-base          = 18px //改成你想要的即可！</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="設置字體顏色"><a href="#設置字體顏色" class="headerlink" title="設置字體顏色"></a>設置字體顏色</h2><p>設定文件的內容顏色！ 文件位置: <code>./themes/next/source/css/_custom/custom.styl</code><br>//修改字體顏色</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">body &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    color: &lt;在這裡填上你想要的顏色，如：<span class="comment">#000&gt;; //別漏了分號！</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>Reference:<br><a href="https://www.jianshu.com/p/e0c5d4d72222" target="_blank" rel="noopener">參考1 霸气龙先森</a><br><a href="https://jacksonleon.gitee.io/posts/1540132352.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">參考2</a><br><a href="http://dinghongkai.com/2017/12/19/Blog-development-6-Customized-Style-of-Writing/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">參考3</a></p>]]></content>
      
      
